OL,3,CWilliam congratulates England on 'top
OL,4,Cperformance' as fans celebrate 2-1
OL,5,Cvictory
OL,7,FThe Prince of Wales has congratulated
OL,8,FEngland on a 2-1 victory against
OL,9,FNorway, which will see the team into
OL,10,Fits first World Cup semi-final since
OL,11,F2018.
OL,13,FA victorious England will face either
OL,14,FArgentina or Switzerland in Atlanta on
OL,15,FWednesday, after a nail-biting quarter-
OL,16,Ffinal saw Jude Bellingham emerge as
OL,17,Fthe star player.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
