CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1783849731
OL,3,CWilliam congratulates England on 'top
OL,4,Cperformance' as fans celebrate 2-1
OL,5,Cvictory
OL,7,FThe midfielder followed up an
OL,8,Fequaliser scored in the first half
OL,9,Fwith the second goal needed to seal
OL,10,Fthe deal and book England a spot in
OL,11,Fthe semi-finals.
OL,13,FWriting on the social media platform
OL,14,FX, William congratulated the team on a
OL,15,F"top performance in a tough
OL,16,Fenvironment" in a personally signed
OL,17,Fmessage.
OL,19,FThe future king wrote: "Well done
OL,20,FEngland! Top performance in a tough
OL,21,Fenvironment. This is a special team.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@LO]{D@XOU
