OL,3,CWilliam congratulates England on 'top
OL,4,Cperformance' as fans celebrate 2-1
OL,5,Cvictory
OL,7,F"Commiserations to a proud Norway
OL,8,Fteam. Onto the semi final... Never in
OL,9,Fdoubt! W"
OL,11,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer joined
OL,12,Fthe prince in congratulating the team,
OL,13,Fand referenced Bjorge Lillelien's
OL,14,Ffamous commentary when Norway beat
OL,15,FEngland 2-1 in a World Cup qualifier
OL,16,Fin 1981.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
