OL,3,CWilliam congratulates England on 'top
OL,4,Cperformance' as fans celebrate 2-1
OL,5,Cvictory
OL,7,FJim Thompson, 57, from Leeds, said he
OL,8,Fplanned on missing the second leg of
OL,9,Fhis flight home to Manchester as his
OL,10,Flayover is in Atlanta.
OL,12,F"I think they can go all the way this
OL,13,Ftime," he said.
OL,15,F"The quality in the squad, it's
OL,16,Fabsolutely fantastic.
OL,18,F"We started off slow but they're
OL,19,Fcoming strong now ` which I knew they
OL,20,Fwould."
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@FO]wD@AOUzD@AOU|D@GO]
