OL,3,CWilliam congratulates England on 'top
OL,4,Cperformance' as fans celebrate 2-1
OL,5,Cvictory
OL,7,FIn London, overjoyed football fans
OL,8,Fbelted out Three Lions and Hey Jude in
OL,9,Fthe Boxpark bar in Wembley.
OL,11,FFabian Maddix, 31, said watching the
OL,12,Fgame was "euphoric", adding: "I had
OL,13,Fhopes but after the first goal went in
OL,14,Ffrom them, I started doubting things,
OL,15,Fbut I always believe."
OL,17,FHe said he is now going to go home and
OL,18,Fcelebrate.
OL,26,@tD@JOUtD@SO]tD@^OUwD@VO]
