OL,3,CWilliam congratulates England on 'top
OL,4,Cperformance' as fans celebrate 2-1
OL,5,Cvictory
OL,7,FFans went silent ` and some put their
OL,8,Fheads in their hands ` after Norway's
OL,9,FAndreas Schjelderup scored a goal in
OL,10,Fthe 36th minute.
OL,12,FBut their disappointment was replaced
OL,13,Fwith celebration after Bellingham
OL,14,Fscored an equaliser just moments
OL,15,Fbefore half-time.
OL,17,FElated fans launched their pints into
OL,18,Fthe air, cheered loudly and jumped
OL,19,Faround before singing a rendition of
OL,20,FHey Jude.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
