OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1783849731
OL,3,CWilliam congratulates England on 'top
OL,4,Cperformance' as fans celebrate 2-1
OL,5,Cvictory
OL,7,FTheir celebrations continued when
OL,8,FBellingham scored again in the third
OL,9,Fminute of extra time.
OL,11,FNumber 10 Downing Street was decorated
OL,12,Fwith St George's flags ahead of the
OL,13,Fmatch.
OL,15,FA silence was held before the match to
OL,16,Fhonour South Africa midfielder Jayden
OL,17,FAdams, who died aged 25, just weeks
OL,18,Fafter featuring in all three of his
OL,19,Fcountry's group matches at the World
OL,20,FCup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
